Sentencas: The electrochemical characteristics of La0.78Sr0.2FeO3-delta (L78SF) and La0.78Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (L78SCF) cathode electrodes interfaced to a double layer Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (CGO)/YSZ electrolyte were studied using cyclic voltammetry, in the temperature range of 600 to 850 degrees C and under flow of 0.7% O-2 in He.
Titulo: Cyclic voltammetry of La0.78Sr0.2FeO3-δ and La0.78Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ electrodes interfaced to CGO/YSZ

Sentencas: The aim was to identify the electrochemical processes taking place under cathodic polarization.
Titulo: Cyclic voltammetry of La0.78Sr0.2FeO3-δ and La0.78Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ electrodes interfaced to CGO/YSZ

Sentencas: Current peaks were observed in the voltammograms, corresponding to potential and currents dependent on scan rate and temperature.
Titulo: Cyclic voltammetry of La0.78Sr0.2FeO3-δ and La0.78Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ electrodes interfaced to CGO/YSZ

Sentencas: The observed cathodic peaks can be related to reduction of the iron or/and cobalt ions but also to the competing reaction of oxygen reduction.
Titulo: Cyclic voltammetry of La0.78Sr0.2FeO3-δ and La0.78Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ electrodes interfaced to CGO/YSZ
